{"tid":94664,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"年 經 ！競 猜 屬 雞 嘅 夏 蕙 姨 今 年 用 乜 造 型 上 頭 炷 香！","createTime":"2017-01-25T11:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T15:33:17.000Z","uid":53178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f86e651d838b0b36a63990acfc6d76321306123","tid":94664,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"大家都知夏蕙姨03年上頭炷香俾人逼甩假髮後，為安全起見，每年初一爭上頭炷香都一定會以造型固定假髮！今年適逢雞年，夏蕙姨仲要屬雞，犯大歲，相信造型一定會十分養眼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我大美人tip呢兩套造型，夠爆！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/193236_102b8a166f7e566f29bbfdef3051781d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F193236_102b8a166f7e566f29bbfdef3051781d.jpg&h=317b9f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/193236_5b68f7e6fb9a56aabaeeaf8797c5af58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F193236_5b68f7e6fb9a56aabaeeaf8797c5af58.jpg&h=e74b2920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">回顧返歷年奇趣造型：</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/191811_923342fa1871b823ae6adf9a7f0b4ced.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F191811_923342fa1871b823ae6adf9a7f0b4ced.jpg&h=d6bbd1e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2013年 蛇年<br />\n霸氣銀蛇頭飾<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXw7mg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXw7mg9.jpg&h=445c4de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2014年 馬年<br />\n人馬合體 crossover 大戲make up<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/191812_413a41fbf0ed5e9dbd80e5f859df0c26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F191812_413a41fbf0ed5e9dbd80e5f859df0c26.jpg&h=c621e44e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2015年 羊年<br />\n純潔小綿羊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i9F02yk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi9F02yk.jpg&h=bd6ae11c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2016年 猴年<br />\n大戲版孫悟空<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/192200_044bbfab0fcc58450bebbb197610aa9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F192200_044bbfab0fcc58450bebbb197610aa9f.jpg&h=d1fa5da9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請 出 招 ！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c44b754aac87165a99a7cc0326a50d38006b39be","tid":94664,"uid":17853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:35:27.000Z","msg":"可能就咁行入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf730dc99a629a804a8347d0b94139a70e339dd2","tid":94664,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能就咁行入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fc2a846cbc2da0d9d80e37d56a3c783a31f28a","tid":94664,"uid":29336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可能就咁行入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d297aeace800ccb62b14541f8eaca5ca2fbc769d","tid":94664,"uid":46842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可能就咁行入去<img src=\"/a